        <content>
          <p>(Ga. L. 1907, p. 72, § 8; Civil Code 1910, § 2665; Code 1933, § 93-414; Ga. L. 1986, p. 1518, § 1; Ga. L. 2011, p. 582, § 1/HB 116; Ga. L. 2012, p. 775, § 46/HB 942.)</p>
          <p>The 2011 amendment,
      effective May 12, 2011, added subsection (g).</p>
          <p>The 2012 amendment,
      effective May 1, 2012, part of an Act to revise, modernize, and correct the Code, revised punctuation in the introductory language of subsection (g).</p>
